8T09:00:00.000Z"],[18,19,20],"fitness","wellness","body-positive",false,"/images/everybody-1.png","Fitness should be about celebrating what your body can do, not changing it to fit an ideal.\n\n![Everybody Moves](/images/everybody-1.png)\n\n## Redefining Fitness\nAll bodies are good bodies. Health looks different for everyone.\n\n## Finding Joy in Movement\nTry different activities until you find what you genuinely enjoy.\n\n## Mental Health Benefits\nMovement provides mood enhancement, stress relief, and improved confidence.\n\nYour body is worthy of movement and care—celebrate it!\n\n![Everybody Moves](/images/everybody-2.png)","src/content/blog/body-positivity-fitness.md","b9ead77539228bf9",{"html":27,"metadata":28},"\u003Cp>Fitness should be about celebrating what your body can do, not changing it to fit an ideal.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/everybody-1.png\" alt=\"Everybody Moves\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"redefining-fitness\">Redefining Fitness\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>All bodies are good bodies. Health looks different for everyone.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"finding-joy-in-movement\">Finding Joy in Movement\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Try different activities until you find what you genuinely enjoy.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"mental-health-benefits\">Mental Health Benefits\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Movement provides mood enhancement, stress relief, and improved confidence.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Your body is worthy of movement and care—celebrate it!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg src=\"/images/everybody-2.png\" alt=\"Everybody Moves\">\u003C/p>",{"headings":29,"localImagePaths":40,"remoteImagePaths":41,"frontmatter":42,"imagePaths":45},[30,34,37],{"depth":31,"slug":32,"text":33},2,"redefining-fitness","Redefining Fitness",{"depth":31,"slug":35,"text":36},"finding-joy-in-movement","Finding Joy in Movement",{"depth":31,"slug":38,"text":39},"mental-health-benefits","Mental Health Benefits",[],[],{"title":14,"description":15,"pubDate":43,"tags":44,"draft":21,"image":22},["Date","2026-